3x 5dBi Detachable Omni Directional Antenna (RP-SMA)
*[http://wiki.openwrt.org/toh/tp-link/tl-wr940n ''TP-LINK TL-WR940N'' on '''OpenWrt''' wiki]
The TP-LINK TL-WR940N is identical to the TL-WR941ND (detachable) except that :the antennas are not detachable and the hardware version is different. :*[[TP-LINK TL-WR940N v1.x]] - [[TP-LINK TL-WR941ND v4.x]] :*[[TP-LINK TL-WR940N v2.x]] - [[TP-LINK TL-WR941ND v5.x]] :*[[TP-LINK TL-WR940N v3.x]] - [[TP-LINK TL-WR941ND v6.x]] This photo was taken from a TP-Link WR940N v3, but I confirmed it has the same PCB.
